Next, let us discuss terry's next bid. there is convention known as "fourth suit forcing" which works very well on this hand. Basically, when partner opens, responder bids a new suit, partner bids another suit, there is only one suit remaining. In this case, that suit is diamonds. The convention is called "fourth suit forcing" because as in this hand diamonds is the 4th suit, and it establishes a game forcing auction. It says nothing about diamonds. All it says is "partner I want to be in game", so we cannot pass below game. |
