NT|
hondo717: So, if dot had a weak hand, but 4 hearts, she knows she can compete to 3 hearts. and if she plays Bergen Raises, she can then bid 3@H with a weak hand, making it much harder for the opponents. The question now is, what do you do with stronger hands and 4 card support. With Bergen Raises, 3@C and 3@D are used to show stronger hands with 4 card support. I prefer what is known as "Reverse Bergen", so I will discuss that first. |
