nt|
hondo717: But, to keep it simple, I recommend you play redouble shows 10 or more points, any other bid shows less than 10 points. Redouble denies 4 spades. There is also a convention known as "Jordan 2NT" which usually is a limit raise and supposed to show 4 spades. So Roberta, after a takeout double should redouble with 10+ points and 3 card support or Jordan 2NT with 10+ points and four card support. Finally, with less than 10 points bid 2 with three card support and 3 with four card support. |
